<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/26387563">如何用思维导图做ppt演示？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2737893" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">请推荐一下直接做ppt演示的思维导图软件，功能即事先做好思维导图内容，单击时出现思维导图的子节点，实现动态演示效果。</div>


</div>
